# Official JavaScript SDK from VISA

It can generate virtual credit cards.

### Usage

Available interfaces:
```ts
export function createVirtualCreditCard(): Promise<CreditCard>;

export type CreditCard = {
    id: number;
    holder: string;
    expiry: Date;
    cvc: number;
};
```

```ts
import { createVirtualCreditCard } from 'visa-client';

const card = await createVirtualCreditCard();
```
